<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Community.css" />
    <title>Community</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="community-container">
      <section class="community-welcome-section">
        <h1>Welcome to the Community</h1>
        <p>
          Join creative minds from around the world in real-time brainstorming
          sessions. Whether you're stuck on an idea or want to spark new ones,
          our AI-powered prompts will get you thinking.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="community-how-it-works">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>⚡ Join or host a live brainstorming session (time-limited)</li>
          <li>🧠 Get a unique AI-generated prompt to kick off your thinking</li>
          <li>💬 Collaborate in real time with other users</li>
          <li>🏁 Wrap up with actionable ideas or save them for later</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="community-guidelines">
        <h2>Community Guidelines</h2>
        <p>Help us keep the space productive and respectful:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Be kind and constructive in feedback</li>
          <li>Stay on topic during sessions</li>
          <li>No spam, offensive content, or AI prompt abuse</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="community-featured-sessions">
        <h2>Featured Sessions</h2>
        <p>Check out some of the most inspiring recent brainstorming topics:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>“How to reinvent remote work culture?”</li>
          <li>“What’s the next big thing in eco-design?”</li>
          <li>“Can AI help reduce food waste globally?”</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="community-get-involved">
        <h2>Get Involved</h2>
        <p>
          Introduce yourself, suggest prompt ideas, or leave feedback in our
          community forum.
        </p>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/tszsTZ3j" class="btn">Visit the Forum</a>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
